headline: Everyone Knows About Nvidia and Palantir. But These Other 3 Stocks Are Quietly Crushing the S&P 500 in 2024 As Well.
summary: There's no way to deny it: 2024 was a stunning year for the stock market.  As of this writing, the S&P 500 is up nearly 28% year to date.  As always, there are stocks significantly outperforming this otherwise impressive return.
